# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezs2.rpy:16
translate portuguese jezs2_21deca6e:

    # det "I went through the police academy right after high school when I was 18, then got a job here in Skyhill. So about five, six years."
    det "Entrei para a academia de polícia logo após o liceu, quando tinha 18 anos, e depois arranjei um emprego aqui em Skyhill. Portanto, há cerca de cinco, seis anos."

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezs2.rpy:17
translate portuguese jezs2_108abd6c:

    # det "There's only ten of us at the station. When I was the rookie, I was stuck doing the street patrols and parking tickets."
    det "Somos apenas dez na esquadra. Quando era novato, ficava preso a fazer patrulhas de rua e multas de estacionamento."

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezs2.rpy:18
translate portuguese jezs2_2d06f5cb:

    # det "But six people retired in the last two years, so now I'm a detective and leading the biggest case at the precinct."
    det "Mas seis pessoas reformaram-se nos últimos dois anos, por isso agora sou detetive e estou a liderar o maior caso da esquadra."

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezs2.rpy:19
translate portuguese jezs2_ec77cfbd:

    # pc "Half the force retiring in two years is pretty unusual, isn't it?"
    pc "Metade da força policial a reformar-se em dois anos é bastante invulgar, não é?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezs2.rpy:21
translate portuguese jezs2_3ffc4d3c:

    # det "Yeah it is."
    det "Sim, é."

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezs2.rpy:22
translate portuguese jezs2_8c877421:

    # det "There has been a lot of stress around the meth ring."
    det "Tem havido muito stress em torno do esquema de metanfetamina."

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezs2.rpy:23
translate portuguese jezs2_0f7b4155:

    # det "It's put a real strain on everybody."
    det "Isso tem colocado uma pressão enorme em toda a gente."

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezs2.rpy:25
translate portuguese jezs2_f9413659:

    # det "But we're getting close. Eventually, we'll catch them and shut them down. Then things can go back to normal around here."
    det "Mas estamos a chegar perto. Eventualmente, vamos apanhá-los e acabar com eles. Aí as coisas podem voltar ao normal por aqui."

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezs2.rpy:26
translate portuguese jezs2_323035f0:

    # det "Then maybe I can take a damn vacation or something."
    det "Aí talvez eu consiga tirar umas férias ou algo do género."

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezs2.rpy:27
translate portuguese jezs2_8d867ef4:

    # pc "You deserve it."
    pc "Mereces."

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezs2.rpy:28
translate portuguese jezs2_4d4b7d71:

    # det "I don't deserve anything until I finish the job."
    det "Não mereço nada até terminar o trabalho."

